('Chimmie Fadden Out West','', ARRAY ['Chimmie is sent out west as part of a scam by a railroad company. He is to pretend to find gold, then retreat as the company takes advantage. Things do not go as planned.[4]'], 'Cecil B. DeMille','Victor Moore','https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Chimmie_Fadden_Out_West_-_newspaper_scene_-_1916.jpg/220px-Chimmie_Fadden_Out_West_-_newspaper_scene_-_1916.jpg','November 21, 1915 (1915-11-21)','$15,096','$72,036'),
